commit.message:
c-semantics.c, [...]: Update copyright.

	* c-semantics.c, cfghooks.c, diagnostic.h, loop-iv.c,
	loop-unswitch.c, modulo-sched.c, stor-layout.c, tree-gimple.h,
	config/i386/cygwin1.c, doc/cfg.texi, doc/objc.texi: Update
	copyright.

From-SVN: r96100
